          <p class="text-on-surface-variant text-lg leading-relaxed">
            We don't just review vehicles; we document the heritage of motion. Each specimen is selected for its soul, its story, and its mechanical purity.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="flex-1 grid grid-cols-2 gap-x-8 md:gap-x-12 gap-y-10 md:gap-y-16">
          <div class="group">
            <div class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-6xl text-primary font-bold mb-2 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-2">124</div>
            <div class="h-px w-full bg-outline-variant/20 mb-4"></div>
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold text-on-surface">Unique Archives</span>
          </div>
          <div class="group">
            <div class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-6xl text-on-surface font-bold mb-2 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-2">08</div>
            <div class="h-px w-full bg-outline-variant/20 mb-4"></div>
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold text-on-surface-variant">Curated Films</span>
          </div>
          <div class="group">
            <div class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-6xl text-on-surface font-bold mb-2 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-2">18</div>
            <div class="h-px w-full bg-outline-variant/20 mb-4"></div>
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold text-on-surface-variant">Global Meets</span>
          </div>
          <div class="group">
            <div class="font-headline text-5xl md:text-6xl text-primary font-bold mb-2 transition-transform group-hover:-translate-y-2">2M+</div>
            <div class="h-px w-full bg-outline-variant/20 mb-4"></div>
            <span class="text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.3em] font-bold text-on-surface">Total Miles</span>
